Documentation
-------------

The SCelVis documentation at `ReadTheDocs.org <https://scelvis.readthedocs.org>`_ contains comprehensive information including a `Tutorial <https://scelvis.readthedocs.io/en/latest/tutorial_analysis.html>`_.

